msgid "Erase 1 tally mark. Remove 1 [skull] from the chaos bag."
msgstr "擦去1次记录。从混乱袋中移除1个[skull]标记。"

msgid ""
"Each investigator may search the collection for a basic [[Pact]], [[Curse]], [[Omen]], or [[Silver Twilight]] weakness of their choice and add it to their deck. Each investigator who does earns 4 bonus experience, which can only be spent to purchase or upgrade [[Spell]], [[Ritual]], [[Sorcerer]], or [[Witch]] cards.\n"
"<i>(Note: the app will not enforce what the XP is spent on.)</i>"
msgstr ""
"每位调查员可以搜索收藏，选择并找出一个[[契约]]、[[诅咒]]、[[征兆]]或[[银暮秘社]]基础弱点，将其加入自己牌组。每位这么做的调查员获得4点奖励经验值，这些经验值只能用于购买或升级[[法术]]、[[仪式]]、[[法师]]或[[女巫]]卡牌。\n"
"<i>(注意：本APP不会强制检查这些经验值花费在哪里。)</i>"

msgid "Accept the knowledge"
msgstr "接受知识"

msgid "Erase 1 tally mark. Add a \"-1\" token to the chaos bag."
msgstr "擦去1次记录。将1个-1标记加入混乱袋。"

msgid "Add 2 [cultist] tokens to the chaos bag. Each investigator begins the next scenario with 2 additional resources and 2 additional cards on their starting hand."
msgstr "将2个[cultist]标记加入混乱袋。在下一场冒险开始时，每位调查员额外获得2资源和2张起始手牌。"
